These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-1::.
There 2 different types of food: orange, grapefruit
2 different games are played: snooker, poker
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, country
There are 2 different nationalities: french, malaysian
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, lily
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, van
1. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
2. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person eating grapefruit is on the far right##1
4. the french is on the right of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Food      | orange       | grapefruit    |
| Game           | poker | snooker |
| Music-Genre   | country     | r&b   |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | french     |
| Flower           | lily       | azalea     |
| Transport     | roller     | van        |

