.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different games are played: canasta, domino
City: paris, nizza
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, crime
There are 2 different nationalities: malaysian, argentine
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: orchid, poppy
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, ship
1. the argentine is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
2. the person playing domino is the argentine##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Game      | canasta        | domino   |
| City         | nizza | paris |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | crime   |
| Nationality   | malaysian       | argentine     |
| Flower           | poppy        | orchid    |
| Transport     | motorbike  | ship    |

