The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, writing
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, train
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, october
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, daffodil
There are 2 different favourite colors: green, aquamarine
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |
| Food          | pepper    | avocado      |
| Hobby         | writing   | baking       |
| Transport   | train | scooter |
| Birthday   | october  | june    |
| Flower           | marigold       | daffodil   |
| Color         | aquamarine   | green     |

